Tallahassee, Florida 32399-1734
[I do not know the details of the study in Sweden but I can assure our
readers that the people involved are as good a group of scientists as one
can find, so I have complete confidence that they have looked at as many
eventualities as possible, including the obvious ones.
As for drinking water with particulates in it: I try to avoid that. Here
in the Rocky Mountains we do not worry so much about viruses emanating from
mountain springs but worry more about _Giardia_ and things that might grow
nicely in an elk carcass floating in a lake. When I backpack with my wife,
I carry the fishing gear and she the 6-pack of Coke and the Gray Poupon. -
Mod.CHC
